# PHP Form with SQL Insert

Here's a complete, secure example using **PDO** with prepared statements (to prevent SQL injection).

## 1. Database Setup (run this SQL first)

```sql
CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS mydb;

USE mydb;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS people (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    age INT NOT NULL,
    sex ENUM('Male', 'Female', 'Other') NOT NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);
```

## 2. Database Connection (`db.php`)

```php
<?php
$host    = 'localhost';
$db      = 'mydb';
$user    = 'root';       // change to your DB username
$pass    = '';           // change to your DB password
$charset = 'utf8mb4';

$dsn = "mysql:host=$host;dbname=$db;charset=$charset";

$options = [
    PDO::ATTR_ERRMODE            => PDO::ERRMODE_EXCEPTION,
    PDO::ATTR_DEFAULT_FETCH_MODE => PDO::FETCH_ASSOC,
    PDO::ATTR_EMULATE_PREPARES   => false,
];

try {
    $pdo = new PDO($dsn, $user, $pass, $options);
} catch (PDOException $e) {
    die("Database connection failed: " . $e->getMessage());
}
?>
```

## 3. Main Script (`index.php`)

```php
<?php
require 'db.php';

$message = '';

if ($_SERVER['REQUEST_METHOD'] === 'POST') {
    // Collect and sanitize input
    $name = trim($_POST['name'] ?? '');
    $age  = $_POST['age'] ?? '';
    $sex  = $_POST['sex'] ?? '';

    // Basic validation
    if ($name === '' || $age === '' || $sex === '') {
        $message = "⚠️ All fields are required.";
    } elseif (!ctype_digit($age) || (int)$age < 0 || (int)$age > 150) {
        $message = "⚠️ Please enter a valid age.";
    } elseif (!in_array($sex, ['Male', 'Female', 'Other'])) {
        $message = "⚠️ Please select a valid sex.";
    } else {
        // Insert using a prepared statement
        $stmt = $pdo->prepare(
            "INSERT INTO people (name, age, sex) VALUES (:name, :age, :sex)"
        );
        $stmt->execute([
            ':name' => $name,
            ':age'  => (int)$age,
            ':sex'  => $sex,
        ]);

        $message = "✅ Record inserted successfully! (ID: " . $pdo->lastInsertId() . ")";
    }
}
?>
